COURSE POLICIES

Attendance and Participation
This is a seminar course where active participation is essential. Students are expected to attend all classes, complete readings before class, and participate in discussions.

Academic Integrity
All work must be your own. Collaboration on problem sets is allowed but must be acknowledged. Plagiarism will result in course failure and disciplinary action.

